<bibRefCitation author="Hoffmann, A" journalOrPublisher="Opuscula Zoologica, Budapest" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" pagination="11 - 29" refId="B29" refString="Hoffmann, A, 1968. The scientific results of the Hungarian soil zoological expedition to the Brazzaville-Congo. 32. Especes de la famille Curculionidae (Coleoptera). Opuscula Zoologica, Budapest 8: 11 - 29" title="The scientific results of the Hungarian soil zoological expedition to the Brazzaville-Congo. 32. Especes de la famille Curculionidae (Coleoptera)." volume="8" year="1968">Hoffmann 1968</bibRefCitation>
: 23 (as subgenus of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bedel" authorityYear="1884" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Anchonidium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Anchonidium" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="syn. nov.">Anchonidium</taxonomicName>
Bedel, 1884; species included: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoffmann" authorityYear="1968" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Anchonidium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Anchonidium baloghi" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baloghi" status="syn. nov.">Anchonidium baloghi</taxonomicName>
). Type species: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoffmann" authorityYear="1968" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Anchonidium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Anchonidium baloghi" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baloghi" status="syn. nov.">Anchonidium baloghi</taxonomicName>
Hoffmann, 1968 by monotypy.
